bomber v 200
bomber owner b1
bomber target t1
bomber program tests\hited.pgm
bomber event HITED hited
hit category/t bomber

b1 base 0 100 40000
b1 angle/a 180

;------------------------- Бой

srand auto

fighter.radar show 0
fighter.control show 9

battle map 8
battle map/c fighter green
